notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the kernel SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 9.4. It addresses 8 CVEs: CVE-2022-50087, CVE-2025-38449, CVE-2025-37823, CVE-2025-38200, CVE-2025-38472, and 3 more.
